_sText:
This is my first released GunGame Map... Its a little Castle on a island. Very much detailed so the fps aren't that good for older PC's. I did what i could for optimizing, read tons of tutorials about optimizing and asked tons of pro mappers but it wouldn't get better than its now! 90% of the Content is Custom. The models are from garysmod.com, the textures are made by myself out of stocks from cgtextures.com Also i have added an overview of the map and many many breakable things in the map, like a door or walls...
Many thanks goes to Beta Testers: This is the new Shit Krusty foxhound-clan Austria Mapping Helpers: Bashor mapping-tutorials.com and my Clan: surf-velocity.org surf-velocity.com
Now have fun and good luck Cu Jacky
